{"article_id":"bpRy83ZOIXwZYOlP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The chairman of the House Intelligence Committee said Sunday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that Syria 's Assad regime has `` absolutely '' crossed the so-called `` red line ''","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"by moving and using at least a small amount of chemical weapons ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"pressuring the Obama administration to get more involved in the conflict","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to prevent further bloodshed .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"`` There is mounting evidence","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that it is probable that the Assad regime has used at least a small quantity of chemical weapons during the course of this conflict , ''","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Rep. Mike Rogers , R-Mich. , said Sunday .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"The comments come","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"a week after both the Assad regime and opposition forces traded charges","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"of using chemical weapons .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Neither claim has been substantiated by U.N. investigators","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"and President Obama has urged caution","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"in assessing the allegations .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"U.S. officials said last week","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"there 's no evidence at this point","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that chemical weapons were used ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"though Obama reiterated during his tour of the Middle East","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"that any use of such weapons would be a `` game-changer . ''","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The administration has long considered chemical weapons to be the `` red line ''","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"which ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"if crossed ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"could trigger military intervention .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Rogers did not say for certain","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"whether the weapons were used last week ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"but said","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"they 've likely been employed since the start of the conflict in 2011 .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Further , he noted","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that the red line had been defined as both moving and using the weapons .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"it is abundantly clear that that red line has been crossed ... absolutely , ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Rogers said on CBS ' `` Face the Nation . ''","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"`` The fact","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that they have ,","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"I think ,","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"put chemical weapons in a position","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"to use","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"and I believe","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"have intent","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"and at some course during the last two years have used some quantity of chemical weapons ,","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"this needs to be a game-changer . ''","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"The congressman told reporters after the Sunday show interview","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that he thinks","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"there is a `` high probability ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"the weapons were used by the Assad regime .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Rogers said","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"this should n't necessarily lead to a `` big boots on the ground conflict , ''","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"but suggested","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"the U.S. send `` small groups with special capabilities ''","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"to re-engage","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and train and equip the opposition .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"`` Indecision in this case is dangerous , ''","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Rogers said .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"`` If Assad goes next week ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"this is mass chaos . ''","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Some U.S. lawmakers have been nudging Obama toward getting more involved in the wake of the chemical weapons reports .","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"Others have urged caution .","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"Officials with the State Department and White House repeatedly stressed this past week","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"that they did n't want to act","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"before knowing all the details","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"about what weapons have been used .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Obama has suggested","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"he does n't want to make Syria and region even more unstable","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"by sending in the U.S. military .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Meanwhile , frustration among the opposition was mounting","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"as the leader of the Western-backed Syrian opposition coalition resigned Sunday ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"citing what he called the lack of international support for those","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"seeking to topple President Bashar Assad .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"The resignation of Mouaz al-Khatib deals a blow to the most credible body","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"seeking to represent the opposition ,","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"which remains deeply divided","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"and continues to struggle to present a united front two years into Syria 's bloody uprising .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Al-Khatib , a respected preacher","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"who has led the Syrian National Coalition since its creation late last year ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"posted on his Facebook page","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that he was making good on a vow","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"to quit","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"if certain undefined `` red lines '' were crossed .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"`` I am keeping my promise today","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and announcing my resignation from the National Coalition","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"so that I can work with freedom","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that is not available inside the official institutions , ''","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"He also blamed world powers for providing insufficient support for the rebel cause","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"and complained","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"that many `` international and regional parties '' insisted on pushing the opposition toward dialogue with the regime .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Most opposition leaders and activists say","depth":3},{"id":88,"text":"Assad 's regime has killed too many people","depth":4},{"id":89,"text":"to be part of a solution to the conflict .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":179,"left":153,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":144,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":103,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":97,"right":102,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":94,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":92,"right":93,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":0,"right":91,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":99,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":8,"right":98,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":11,"right":100,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":111,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":107,"right":110,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"